data.title: 121newsonline.com: After ‘Dil Warda’ AJ Singh is Back with Beat Number ‘Biba’
data.meta_description: 121newsonline,Chandigarh News, 121news, news, Tricity News, Mohali, Punjab
data.text:
By 121 News

Chandigarh 01st November:- Survival in the world of entertainment is not everyone's cup of tea. One needs constant support during the initial years to make it in the long run. And one such music channel which always has the back of its artists is T-Series, one of the oldest music channels in the country. And now this music label has released the song titled 'Biba'.

The song has been sung by AJ Singh. The lyrics of the song are penned by Diljan. Music has been composed by Showkidd/Lakshay. The video of the song has been helmed by Team DG. The female lead in the song is Manisha Kaushal. The entire project has been produced by T-Series. The song has already released on the YouTube channel of T-Series Apna Punjab.

On this occasion, AJ Singh said that he is living his dream because becoming a singer was his childhood dream. He don't restrict himself to only singing but also put forth his suggestions which can turn the things in the best of the team's interest. He hope people will like the song as much as we do.

The director of the video, Team DG, said that still pretty new in the industry, we prefer quality over quantity. The entire team has put in a lot of effort, and just hope that the masses give a big fat thumbs up to the song.

The producer of the song, T-Series said that AJ Singh is a very talented artist of the industry who if given constant motivation will surely win over the hearts of the people. We are happy that we got the chance to work with him. We hope that the audience lauds his talent and shower their love as they have previously.

AJ Singh has previously released 'Dil Warda', 'Neeli Neeli Aankhen' and 'Top Notch' to name a few.
